data.description: Welcome to your dream home in the Hidden Lake community located in the heart of Ruskin, Florida. This beautiful residence offers the perfect blend of comfort, style, and convenience, making it an ideal place to call home.  This spacious property has three bedrooms, two baths providing ample space for your family and guests. Each bedroom is designed with relaxation in mind, featuring large windows that allow natural light to flow throughout the rooms. The open concept living area is perfect for entertaining. The living room features bright lighting that offer serene views, while the adjacent dining area provides an inviting space for gatherings. You will fall in love with spacious eat in kitchen whether you're preparing a quick breakfast or a gourmet dinner, this kitchen has everything you need. Situated in the heart of Ruskin, you'll have easy access to shopping, dining, schools, and entertainment options. The nearby beaches of Tampa Bay and the Gulf of Mexico are just a short drive away, allowing you to enjoy the Florida coastal lifestyle. Don't miss the opportunity to make this 3/2 bath gem in Hidden Lake your new home.  It's convenient location, and serene surroundings, it offers the best of Florida living. Schedule a showing today and experience the beauty and comfort this property has to offer.
